{"lastModified":1764337313765,"uri":"c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: U.S. Virgin Islands, British Virgin Islands, Leeward Islands, Windward Islands\n\nEPIPHANY is a 17.07m / 56ft Catamaran Luxury Yacht built in 2023 by Bali Catamarans. Sleeping 10 guests in 5 cabins and with a crew of 2. The guest cabins comprise of 5 cabins with a queen size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"EPIPHANY","images":["/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::9d251dc0-1496-11ef-a805-7b2c3c9892e0.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::e89355b0-a9a2-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::eba52990-a9a2-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::ea8365e0-a9a2-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::df195700-a9a2-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::2d0f2070-a9a8-11ee-9d27-b77f8c5bcf6f.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::e7549420-a9a2-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::e2905550-a9a2-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::e663f290-a9a2-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::e58d1a90-a9a2-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c