"},{"label":"Hairdryers","quantity":""},{"label":"Inverter","quantity":""},{"label":"BBQ","quantity":""},{"label":"Sailing Instructions","quantity":""},{"label":"iPod/Device Hookups","quantity":""},{"label":"Deck shower","quantity":""},{"label":"Water Maker","quantity":""},{"label":"Wi-Fi","quantity":""},{"label":"Bimini","quantity":""}],"toys":[{"label":"Dinghy","quantity":8},{"label":"Kneeboard","quantity":""},{"label":"Snorkel Gear","quantity":""},{"label":"Tube","quantity":""},{"label":"Kayaks (2 Pax)","quantity":""},{"label":"Floating Mats","quantity":""},{"label":"Swim Platform","quantity":""},{"label":"Boarding Ladder","quantity":""},{"label":"Beach Games","quantity":""},{"label":"SU Paddle Boards","quantity":""},{"label":"Underwater Camera","quantity":""},{"label":"Underwater Video","quantity":""},{"label":"Sea Scooters","quantity":""}],"entertainment":["Salon TV","Salon Stereo","iPod/Device Hookups","Wi-Fi"],"tenders":["Tender with 60 HP engine"]},"crew":[{"name":"Adam Grant","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::c2a6a650-b1c1-11ee-8f26-4783612135e1.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"With a decade of navigating the world's waters, Captain Adam Grant brings an unparalleled wealth of expertise and a contagious enthusiasm for the sea. His maritime journey has taken him across diverse landscapes, from the azure waters of Greece and the Caribbean to the captivating coasts of Central America and Sweden.\n\nExperience & Versatility\nAdam's diverse background spans various roles within the maritime industry. As a seasoned charter captain, commercial captain on dive, fishing, and marine surveying boats, he has honed his skills in managing and navigating a wide array of vessels, each with its unique demands and challenges. His proficiency and adaptability in different maritime settings stand testament to his versatile expertise.\n\nDive Instruction & Technical Aptitude\nBeyond the helm, Adam is also a proficient dive instructor, boasting five years of guiding and teaching experience beneath the waves. His dedication to imparting his deep love for the ocean extends beyond sailing; he fosters a deep appreciation for marine life and ecosystems through his insightful instruction.\n\nMechanical Proficiency & Boat Yard Experience\nAdam's foundation in the industry goes beyond steering vessels. He apprenticed as a technician in a boat yard, cultivating a robust mechanical background. This hands-on experience provides him with a keen understanding of the intricacies of boats, ensuring not just smooth sailing but also adept handling of any mechanical challenges that might arise.\n\nCommitment to Service Excellence\nWhat truly sets Captain Grant apart is his unwavering commitment to service excellence. His focus on providing exceptional experiences, coupled with his innate hospitality, ensures every charter with him is nothing short of extraordinary. Whether it's creating bespoke dive adventures or tailoring fishing expeditions, Adam's dedication to personalized, top-tier service is unmatched.\n\nFor Captain Adam Grant, every voyage is an opportunity to share his passion for the sea, offer unparalleled experiences, and forge lasting memories. With a combination of expertise, a welcoming demeanor, and an unwavering commitment to service, he invites you to embark on a journey of discovery and delight on the open waters.\n\nJoin Captain Grant for an unforgettable maritime adventure!"},{"name":"Jelena Perkovic","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::92570f10-a99e-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b::assets::c8b71430-b1c1-11ee-8f26-4783612135e1.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Chef","bio":"I'm Jelena Perković a 25 year old culinary enthusiast from the capital of Croatia, Zagreb.\nMy academic journey led me to a master's degree on the faculty of kinesiology, the place that introduced me to the world of sailing. I really loved that experience, so I choose sailing as a specialization when I was on my fourth year of studies. In 2021, I started working on a catamaran as a guide/stew. That position allowed me to combine my love for physical activity and cooking. I quickly adapted to the unique demands of life at sea and became a solo stewardess. I was working as a solo stewardess last two seasons on the Adriatic sea. Mostly on catamarans ( Lagoon 46, Saona 47, Aura 51, Bali 5.4 etc) but also some sailboats and motor yachts. One of intersecting things in 2023 was my participation in \"Survivor Croatia“ that was filming in the Dominican Republic. This experience tested my physical and mental resilience and taught me the importance of positive attitude and adaptability. I was taekwondo athlete for 10 years and then 2 years of track & field so I am still living a healthy lifestyle. I am passionate about cooking and continuously seeking new knowledge and techniques in culinary world. I look forward to the opportunity to creating a magical trip for our guests aboard Epiphany!"}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"USD","price":2600000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":2600000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"USD","price":3200000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":3200000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Summer/Winter: Caribbean - Low Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"note":"","currency":"USD","inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","subTotal":2600000,"totalTax":0,"total":2600000,"lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","conditions":"VAT & APA Excluded","quantity":1,"unitPrice":2600000,"amount":2600000}],"charterFee":2600000,"unit":"WEEK"},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"U.S. Virgin Is.","type":"Dependency","category":["North America","Caribbean","U.S. Virgin Is."],"coordinates":[-64.79221690684143,18.050874527948764],"bbox":[-65.0